Program
The aim of the software is to help users learn and practice words in foreign languages. 
User management
The user can create themselves an account. From this account page the user can edit their details and add words. 
Session
The software uses words and their translation given by the user in self-generated learning/practicing sessions. A session consists of a set amount of words given in one language to which the user shall provide the match in their own language to. By tracking the times a given word was answered correctly/incorrectly by the user, the software will 
